title: Psychic Brood
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

If a brood of [[Zoanthrope]]s uses the [[Warp Blast]] power, the number of shots fired is equal to the number of [[Zoanthrope]]s and ''Neurothrope''s in that brood.

>For example, a brood of three [[Zoanthrope]]s that successfully manifested [[Warp Blast]] would treat both the Burst and Lance profiles as [[Assault]] 3.